OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FThe possibility of Heathrow Airport
OL,7,Fbeing expanded by a rival company has
OL,8,Fmoved a step closer.
OL,10,FThe Civil Aviation Authority (CAA) has
OL,11,Fsaid that an alternative developer
OL,12,Fmodel is among four shortlisted
OL,13,Foptions for how the west London
OL,14,Fairport could boost its capacity.
OL,16,FIt would be consistent with the
OL,17,FHeathrow West proposal by hotel tycoon
OL,18,FSurinder Arora's company, Arora Group,
OL,19,Fto build, own and operate a third
OL,20,Frunway and new terminal at Heathrow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
