FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FThe airport's owners - Heathrow
OL,7,FAirport Limited (HAL) - are keen to
OL,8,Fobtain permission to deliver the
OL,9,Fexpansion project themselves, arguing
OL,10,Fthat a single body maintaining control
OL,11,Fof all terminals would be more
OL,12,Fefficient.
OL,14,FAn alternative developer would be in
OL,15,Fdirect competition to HAL, which
OL,16,Flargely consists of overseas
OL,17,Finvestors, led by private equity giant
OL,18,FArdian and the sovereign wealth funds
OL,19,Fof Qatar and Saudi Arabia.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FThe implementation of this regulatory
OL,7,Fmodel would be dependent on amendments
OL,8,Fto the government's Airports National
OL,9,FPolicy Statement (ANPS) - which are
OL,10,Fset to be consulted on by July - and a
OL,11,Fdeveloper obtaining planning
OL,12,Fpermission.
OL,14,FOther shortlisted options include
OL,15,Fimproving the existing framework for
OL,16,Fregulating the airport, such as more
OL,17,Fscrutiny of spending, and a model to
OL,18,Fsupport cost effective longer-term
OL,19,Ffinancing at the airport.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FThe final option would create new
OL,7,Fobligations on HAL to competitively
OL,8,Ftender elements of expansion -
OL,9,Fpotentially resulting in a third party
OL,10,Fdesigning and building assets - while
OL,11,Fretaining overall responsibility for
OL,12,Fcoordinating and financing the work.
OL,14,FA consultation on the shortlist will
OL,15,Frun until Monday, June 15.
OL,17,FArora Group previously said it wanted
OL,18,Fto install a 2,800-metre new runway at
OL,19,FHeathrow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
