OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FThat would not require moving the M25
OL,7,Fmotorway, unlike the airport's own
OL,8,Fplan to build a full-length, 3,500-
OL,9,Fmetre runway.
OL,11,FIn November, Transport Secretary Heidi
OL,12,FAlexander announced her preference for
OL,13,Fa full-length runway.
OL,15,FHAL's scheme is estimated to cost #33
OL,16,Fbillion, including #1.5 billion to
OL,17,Fmove the M25, and is expected to be
OL,18,Ffully privately financed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,FIt would see Heathrow's capacity
OL,7,Fincrease to 756,000 flights and 150
OL,8,Fmillion passengers per year.
OL,10,FA Heathrow spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Heathrow's success as one of the
OL,12,Fworld's top and most punctual airports
OL,13,Fis built on private investment and
OL,14,Fstrong airline partnerships.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
