OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778929376
OL,3,CHeathrow expansion could be done by
OL,4,Crival company, says aviation regulator
OL,6,F"We support reform that boosts
OL,7,Fefficiency, cuts red tape and keeps
OL,8,Finvestment flowing, but not proposals
OL,9,Fwhich will undermine our efforts to
OL,10,Fimprove the airport for consumers or
OL,11,Fdelay the economic growth the country
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,F"We look forward to working with
OL,15,Fgovernment and the regulator to turn
OL,16,Fthese proposals into positive
OL,17,Foutcomes."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
